event.title: Teppanyaki or All You Can Eat
event.description:
Previously Yamagata Teppanyaki, we have added an All You Can Eat option while retaining our prized Teppanyaki experience in our committment to bringing you the best of both worlds.
Looking for Japanese Cuisine? This is the place to be!

Teppanyaki
-----------------
We will carry on Yamagata’s renowned Teppanyaki experience, giving you an unforgettable night. Our talented chefs will entertain you with a fiery show of skill while they cook your meal before your eyes! Perfect for a special night out, celebrations, corporate events or just having an enjoyable meal out with family and friends. A premium experience when only the best will do!

All you Can Eat
----------------------
Introducing an all new extensive menu selection for All You Can Eat! Freshly made to order Sushi, Sashimi, Tempura, and a whole range of choices from familiar favourites to amazing chef specials, not to mention irrisistable desserts too! An absolutely delicious feast with incredible value.

event.title: Limited Release Coffee IPA by Cavalier and Proud Mary
event.description:
For a limited time check out the brand new Black Coffee IPA by local Melbourne brewery Cavalier in collaboration with the popular Proud Mary Coffee.

Natural process coffee from Yirgacheffe, Ethiopia with natural stone fruit characteristics create a big coffee hit followed by a fresh, citrus, pine and resin hop flavour.

Check out this strong 6.6% beer for only $9 a schooner. Great value, but once the keg runs out, that's it!
